response.overview: In this special prequel episode, Samantha 'Atom Eve' Wilkins discovers her superpowers as a young girl - and must come to terms with her own sinister origins as she discovers a family she never knew she had.  This one-off special reveals how Atom Eve of the Invincible universe got her powers, and her early days as she became a superhero and became the crimefighting juggernaut that she grew up to be, along with her family trials and tribulations.
response.title: Invincible: Atom Eve
